'''Ulaanbaatar Broadcasting System''' ({{lang-mn|Улаанбаатар телевиз}}), or '''UBS''', is a [[television]] broadcaster in [[Mongolia]]. It operates three channels, '''UBS''' which is the main channel, '''UBS Global''' and '''UBS Music Channel'''.
